metadata.name: Aligned
metadata.description:
Isn’t it wonderful? How sometimes things happen so naturally, yet so perfectly and sublimely?

This is one of those moments which I got to gracefully experience through my camera’s viewfinder while snapping this amazing pair of giraffes.

From the lovely patterns, the elegant details and texture, the fur and the rare presence of these beautiful, tall creatures, you can’t help but gaze in awe.
